br.ufrj.ct.restauranteuniversitario

Class Ticket

  • java.lang.Object
    • br.ufrj.ct.restauranteuniversitario.Ticket

  • public class Ticket
extends java.lang.Object
    Created by Felipe Podolan Oliveira on 20/03/17. This is the Ticket class, with same attributes as the backend. The attributes are named in a maner that it facilitates the conversion of a Ticket object and a ticket json (received from the backend) by using the Gson library.
